Module frameDemo2

Package frameDemo2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    cashRegister
    cash register class that keeps track of the cost/prices of orders and number of orders
    CoffeeItem
    coffee sub classs that extends the drink item superclass and holds the customizations for the coffee order
    coffeePurchaseFrame
    the coffee frame that will display options for customizing the coffee item and extends the newItemFrame
    DrinkItem
    the drink item sub class that extends the item superclass used for generic drink things
    finalizeFrame
    sets up the final frame made for entering the payment.
    Item
    item superclass that contains generic things like the item name and the cost of the item
    newItemFrame
    sets up the new order frame made for displaying the receipt.
    newPurchase
    main class that begins the entire process
    PastryItem
    pastry item sub class that extends the item superclass used to create pastry order
    PastryPurchaseFrame
    pastry frame used to create and add pastrys to the order
    startFrame
    the starting frame that extends JFrame and contains only 3 buttons and a hidden done button
    TeaItem
    sub class tea item that extends the drink item superclass and keeps track of the drink item created.
    TeaPurchaseFrame
    the tea frame that will display options for customizing the tea item and extends the newItemFrame
    thankYouFrame
    last frame that displays the amount of change given back and a thank you message and has a exit button that terminates the program this extends the finalize frame
